      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TIGGERLONG BINGO (3) won by 8 lengths last start when getting around this track 320m in a lightning 17.98. Has the ability and expected to go close again. CAWBOURNE SASSY (1) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at this track over 320m behind Bronte Lee (19.14) in a NG. The form out of her last race has been franked. In the mix. ROSES RING (2) has been in super consistent form, finishing in the minors at her last four runs. Last time finished 2nd in a Mix 1/2/3 on January 9 over 350m at Goulburn behind Nangar Archie beaten 1.5 lengths (20.03). Likely to be in the finish again. ROWAN (5) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
